Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.62,00:00:11.62,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,For all people, east to west, west to east, \Ntell a fortune and blow off steam.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.62,00:00:21.00,Caption,,0,0,0,,Invocations
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.62,00:00:17.29,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,This is just one example of the invocations recited \Nwhen you begin divining, as I'm sure you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,00:00:21.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Today, you're going to memorize all of them for a test.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,00:00:22.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.75,00:00:24.87,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,There are ten chapters and \Na hundred verses for all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.87,00:00:26.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There's no way we can memorize all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.33,00:00:30.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm bad enough already with ancient words like these!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.95,00:00:34.79,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,This exam is a tough hurdle \Nall Rank 10 Urara must overcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.16,00:00:39.12,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,If you can't pass it, \Nyou'll never become a full-fledged Urara.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.87,00:00:40.25,Caption,,0,0,0,,Hurdle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.33,00:00:42.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You could say it's your first big hurdle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,00:00:46.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I-it's alright. We can make it through this challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.58,00:00:48.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we can do it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.08,00:00:51.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's work real hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.41,00:00:52.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.62,00:00:55.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Study hard for the test, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.16,00:01:02.25,Caption,,0,0,0,,Crystal Fortunes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.16,00:01:02.25,Caption2,,0,0,0,,ASTROLOGY
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.16,00:01:02.25,Caption3,,0,0,0,,Kokkuri
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.16,00:01:02.25,Caption4,,0,0,0,,DANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.17,00:01:02.25,Caption5,,0,0,0,,FORTUNES
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.17,00:01:02.25,Caption6,,0,0,0,,TEAR READING
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.17,00:01:02.25,Caption7,,0,0,0,,DREAM FORTUNES
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.29,00:01:02.25,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, people lose their way \Nto their fate, or the crossroads of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.37,00:01:06.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,as they wander through the maze of their everyday lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,00:01:08.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,In those times,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.87,00:01:11.33,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,a diviner can present you with an arrow \Npointing to the right choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.83,00:01:17.20,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,The magical power that points the way \Nis sometimes panacea, sometimes poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.66,00:01:21.95,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,To possess that power, one must be a girl \Nwho has passed her fifteenth birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.66,00:01:27.62,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,The girls in this fortune-telling town \Nare sometimes goddesses, sometimes witches.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.00,00:01:28.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Urara!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.91,00:01:34.04,Song,,0,0,0,,I want to make my dreams come true
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.04,00:01:36.79,Song,,0,0,0,,So I'll give it my all again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.87,00:01:42.87,Song,,0,0,0,,When I get lost, I'll ask the gods to help me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.87,00:01:46.83,Song,,0,0,0,,See, you can see a light! Which way? (That way!)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,00:01:50.20,Song,,0,0,0,,Believe in yourself and march on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.58,00:01:54.58,Song,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four, five, six! Jan-jan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.58,00:01:57.87,Song,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four, five, six! Jan-jan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.87,00:02:03.45,Song,,0,0,0,,Which way should I go? I can't decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.00,00:02:09.04,Song,,0,0,0,,The path to our dreams is always a big labyrinth
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.54,00:02:12.37,Song,,0,0,0,,To the left? To the right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,00:02:15.29,Song,,0,0,0,,Which way is right? (Which way?)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.54,00:02:18.16,Song,,0,0,0,,No matter which way I go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,00:02:22.29,Song,,0,0,0,,It'll be fun because my friends are there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.54,00:02:24.37,Song,,0,0,0,,That's the right answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.37,00:02:27.29,Song,,0,0,0,,I want to make my dreams come true
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.29,00:02:30.16,Song,,0,0,0,,So I'll give it my all again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.16,00:02:35.91,Song,,0,0,0,,When I get lost, I'll ask the gods to help me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.20,00:02:41.95,Song,,0,0,0,,See, you can see the future! Let's walk together!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.16,00:02:46.45,Song,,0,0,0,,See, you can see a smile! Which way? (This way!)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.45,00:02:49.62,Song,,0,0,0,,Believe in yourself and march on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.87,00:02:53.87,Song,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four, five, six! Jan-jan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,00:02:57.08,Song,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four, five, six! Jan-jan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,00:03:04.62,Caption,,0,0,0,,ONE DAY
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,00:03:04.62,Caption2,,0,0,0,,UNTIL THE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,00:03:04.62,Caption3,,0,0,0,,INVOCATION
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,00:03:04.62,Caption4,,0,0,0,,MEMORIZATION
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,00:03:04.62,Caption5,,0,0,0,,TEST
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.04,00:03:04.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"Humble, so humble, we b... beseech of thee."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,00:03:09.83,Caption,,0,0,0,,I give up~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,00:03:08.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"Dost thy presence be made... as a water strider..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,00:03:09.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Chiya and Nono broke down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,00:03:11.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Seek to calm thyselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,00:03:15.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This is naught but a test all Urara must weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,00:03:17.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Verily, it is of no difficulty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.37,00:03:18.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Kon broke down, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.79,00:03:22.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My, seems you're all working quite hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,00:03:23.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nina-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.75,00:03:26.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But you're not the only ones who are hurting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,00:03:32.00,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I haven't eaten at all today, \Nin an attempt to share your suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,00:03:35.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nina-sensei, would you like some?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.25,00:03:36.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Get a hold of yourself, Kon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.08,00:03:38.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You too, Nina-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.04,00:03:41.70,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Don't skip out on eating! \NJust tell us tricks on how to memorize them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,00:03:44.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.54,00:03:47.20,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I went through a lot of trouble \Nmemorizing all of them, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,00:03:53.00,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I cut myself off from sweets, I sat under a waterfall, \Nand I stopped Saku's sword mid-swing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,00:03:54.54,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,What does any of this have to do \Nwith memorizing phrases?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,00:03:58.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So I'm painfully aware of your suffering right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.20,00:04:00.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'd like you to suffer more!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,00:04:03.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Guess she likes suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,00:04:11.29,Caption,,0,0,0,,CHAPTER
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,00:04:11.29,Caption2,,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,00:04:07.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Anyway, why do invocations use all these ancient words?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.25,00:04:09.79,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,If they used cute words, \Nthey'd be super easy to memorize!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,00:04:11.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,00:04:15.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,O suffering, confused, lost little lamb.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,00:04:19.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I will divine your path by the name of Miss Plum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.33,00:04:21.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Eloim, eloim, essaim!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.45,00:04:23.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Howl, my grimoire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,00:04:24.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.58,00:04:25.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,00:04:26.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So hard to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,00:04:27.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,00:04:29.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then what kind of invocation would you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,00:04:33.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I think the old, traditional invocations are just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,00:04:36.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Like "kokkuri, kokkuri, please come forth."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,00:04:38.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hmph. How naive, Kon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.62,00:04:39.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wh-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,00:04:42.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We're living in an era where it's every Urara for herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.29,00:04:46.41,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,You have to make yourself stand out from the crowd, \Nor you won't last long!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,00:04:49.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Kokkuri, kokkuri, welcome, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,00:04:51.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Bark!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,00:04:52.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,00:04:53.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How about no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,00:04:56.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I-I'd like them to be a little easier to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.95,00:05:01.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Right?! Make them shorter and easier, and way cooler!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.25,00:05:02.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.33,00:05:03.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.29,00:05:05.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Crow like a rooster!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.29,00:05:07.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.33,00:05:09.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,...that'd be hard for a human to pull off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,00:05:12.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Come, now, put your mind to your studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,00:05:14.83,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry! \NYou shouldn't make light of the sacred invocations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,00:05:19.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sacred? I thought the invocations were just wordplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,00:05:22.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My, you've got that all wrong, Koume-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,00:05:25.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Urara borrow the power of a god to tell fortunes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,00:05:29.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Invocations tell the god that you're going to tell a fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,00:05:33.62,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,They're special words that ask the god \Nthe favor of borrowing their power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.75,00:05:35.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I will now boil something within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,00:05:37.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Please lend me some soy sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,00:05:38.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,00:05:42.08,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Could you have used a \Nmore divine object in your example?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,00:05:47.58,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,The words you use for the invocation \Naren't what's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.04,00:05:52.04,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,What's important is to pour your heart into \Nexpressing your feelings to the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,00:05:56.33,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,If you can do that, then you can use \Nwhatever words or methods you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,00:06:00.66,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,There are scores of different invocations \Nthat Urara use today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,00:06:01.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.08,00:06:05.50,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Oh! So then we don't need to memorize \Nfrom this book, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,00:06:07.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's it for studying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,00:06:11.37,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Memorizing the standard invocations \Nis part of the basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,00:06:14.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The basics are always important.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,00:06:18.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Alright, everyone, good luck on the exam tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.12,00:06:23.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ugh, I really don't feel like memorizing all of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.45,00:06:25.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But I feel a little better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.95,00:06:29.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you talk to the gods, they'll understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.29,00:06:31.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thinking about that makes me wanna study!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,00:06:35.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I-I have a hard time talking to strangers...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,00:06:37.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Now we've got a new problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,00:06:41.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I never thought Nono'd be this shy with the gods, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.37,00:06:46.25,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Not being able to even recite the invocations \Nis a bigger problem than the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.66,00:06:50.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay! Let's all help Nono overcome her shyness!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.04,00:06:51.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,00:06:54.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?! N-no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,00:06:57.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,U-um, you all have to study, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.70,00:07:00.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And, and... it's my problem, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,00:07:06.70,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I think it's a challenge I have to get through myself \Nif I'm going to mature!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,00:07:08.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's caving in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,00:07:10.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nono's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,00:07:16.75,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,It might seem mean, but even though \Nwe're friends, we're rivals, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,00:07:26.12,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,As Urara, we're going to face a lot more challenges, \Nand we have to get through them by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.29,00:07:30.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I respect Nono's courage in tackling her personal issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,00:07:31.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's both work hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.12,00:07:33.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Kon-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,00:07:39.12,Caption,,0,0,0,,MEMORIZE!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,00:07:37.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And to be honest, we don't have a lot of time today
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.71,00:07:37.37,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,to be helping other people out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,00:07:38.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.95,00:07:44.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've gotta work hard, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,00:07:47.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,00:07:55.95,Caption,,0,0,0,,MEMORIZE!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,00:07:59.04,Song,,0,0,0,,Hito futa mi yo, itsu mu nana ya, kokono tari,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,00:07:59.04,Song2,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight, nine, ten,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,00:08:06.70,Song,,0,0,0,,Furube yura yura to, furube yura...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,00:08:06.70,Song2,,0,0,0,,Spring forth, cry out, O spirits...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,00:08:02.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I feel my exhaustion melting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,00:08:04.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm getting kinda sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,00:08:07.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Kon! When did return to normal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.20,00:08:09.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,S-sorry to start singing all of a sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.12,00:08:13.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, Nono, you're a really good singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,00:08:15.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What song was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.50,00:08:21.33,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I don't remember where it's from, but \Nlooking at this invocation made me remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,00:08:26.58,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,It's an invocation that cures illness \Nand fills one with energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.83,00:08:31.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I read in a book that it's used as a lullaby, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,00:08:33.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I can see why.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.75,00:08:34.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wake up, Chiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,00:08:36.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, a lullaby?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.75,00:08:43.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,...itsu mu nana ya, kokono tari...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,00:08:47.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Big Sister, what song is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,00:08:50.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I feel like I heard it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.58,00:08:51.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.37,00:08:55.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's a magic song that makes you feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,00:09:02.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Mom and I sang it to you when you were little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.41,00:09:05.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She sang it so you'd grow up healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,00:09:10.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My mom sang this song to me when I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.70,00:09:13.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nono, your mom passed away, right...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.33,00:09:17.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, when I was just a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,00:09:21.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's why I don't have a lot of memories of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,00:09:26.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Somehow, I remember this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,00:09:33.00,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I bet your mom really loved you, Nono! \NShe put her heart into that song!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.66,00:09:39.54,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,You were too little to understand what she was saying, \Nbut you understood her feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,00:09:41.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.79,00:09:43.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Moms really are nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,00:09:46.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,00:09:49.25,Caption,,0,0,0,,THE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,00:09:49.25,Caption2,,0,0,0,,NEXT
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,00:09:49.25,Caption3,,0,0,0,,DAY
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.08,00:09:49.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay, last up is you, Nono.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.37,00:09:53.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Chapter 5, verse 4,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,00:09:56.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,the nightgown divination invocation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,00:09:57.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,R-right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,00:10:08.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Please, tell me what I do not know
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,00:10:13.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A child, tossing and turning to sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,00:10:20.08,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,As a tempest of dreams tosses \Nand turns the mind in the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.58,00:10:24.20,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,After an all-nighter, that angelic voice \Nis working way too well!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,00:10:25.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I can't take it anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,00:10:28.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We're in the middle of an exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.41,00:10:30.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But tell me, Nono...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.20,00:10:33.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why did you put the invocation to a song?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.41,00:10:38.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,U-umm, I'm still nervous about talking to the gods,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,00:10:41.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but I feel like I can do it in a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.83,00:10:47.87,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I see. You've found your own personal way \Nof expressing your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,00:10:51.70,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Right, that means Chiya-chan and Koume-chan \Nwill have to retake the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,00:10:55.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Go back through and memorize it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,00:10:57.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.41,00:11:01.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Big Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,00:11:04.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What is it, Nono?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.08,00:11:11.75,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Umm, thank you for singing to me with Mom \Nwhen I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,00:11:20.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm going to work hard and become a full-fledged Urara.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.08,00:11:23.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Just you watch, Nina-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,00:11:29.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nina, sorry to barge in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,00:11:31.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is it okay if I have dinner h-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,00:11:35.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wh-wh-what?! What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.91,00:11:37.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.45,00:11:41.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Just stay with me till morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,00:11:42.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.12,00:11:46.70,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I'm happy that Nono's growing up so fast, \Nbut I'm kinda sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.70,00:11:49.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But I also think I should work even harder as her teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,00:11:53.33,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, I'll hear you out, just calm down! \NBut I also think I should work even harder as her teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.66,00:11:58.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nono's invocation was beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.20,00:12:00.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I can't let her beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,00:12:06.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Please, tell me what I do not know
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.29,00:12:10.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A child, tossing and turning to sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,00:12:12.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's kinda different.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,00:12:15.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This way's cuter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.66,00:12:23.16,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Ever since I was little, \NI could always get what I wanted very easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.79,00:12:26.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Enchant√©, mademoiselle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,00:12:32.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But there was one thing I could never get...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,00:12:37.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The one I hate the most...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.25,00:12:40.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,the one I love the most in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.16,00:12:44.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Today's lesson is about witches.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.54,00:12:46.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Does everyone know what a witch is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,00:12:47.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,00:12:51.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Witches are fortune-tellers, and are also called healers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,00:12:53.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You could say they're the Urara of the West!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,00:12:55.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They ride brooms and fly through the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,00:12:58.62,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,and some say they use magic to \Nput curses on people who anger them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,00:13:00.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Excellent answer as always, Kon-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.58,00:13:01.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You sure are worked up for this lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.29,00:13:03.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,O-oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.62,00:13:06.83,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I'd say that Koume is the most worked up \Nabout this lesson out of all of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.83,00:13:17.00,Caption,,0,0,0,,AUTHENTIC
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.83,00:13:17.00,Caption2,,0,0,0,,ATTIRE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.83,00:13:10.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My, Koume, you really love witches, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,00:13:12.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,L-LOVE?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.66,00:13:15.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I-i-it's not like I love them or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,00:13:17.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hard to protest when you're dressed like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.41,00:13:22.41,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I-I mean, witches are cruel and glamorous, \Nand wicked and elegant,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.41,00:13:25.25,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,and rebellious and shameless, \Nand intelligent and invincible,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,00:13:27.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,so there's no way I'd love them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.12,00:13:28.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Which is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,00:13:33.95,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,And I didn't read anything about witches \Nbeing like that. How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,00:13:39.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Well, because I've met a real one. A real witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,00:13:42.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Tell us about her! Tell us about the witch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.95,00:13:44.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I wanna know, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.62,00:13:46.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,W-well, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.79,00:13:48.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,00:13:54.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,When I was five years old...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,00:13:57.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Koume.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,00:14:00.70,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,This girl here is an exchange student from another land, \Nand she'll be living with us from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.95,00:14:03.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She's from a far-off place called France.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.62,00:14:10.62,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Her name was Marie Quispilquette, \Nand she was the first foreigner I'd ever met.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,00:14:12.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And the first witch, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,00:14:13.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Prune.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,00:14:16.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"P-Prune"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,00:14:19.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's how we say "plum" in my country.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.20,00:14:20.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,"Pu" for short!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.33,00:14:24.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sh-she kissed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.37,00:14:26.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That was a cursed kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.29,00:14:28.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's how witches say hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,00:14:30.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wh-wh-wh-what the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.29,00:14:32.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A curse?! What's going to happen to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.54,00:14:34.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're going to be really good friends with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,00:14:39.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And since I'm here, I might as well stay in Pu's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.66,00:14:41.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, go right ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.66,00:14:42.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Right, Koume?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.41,00:14:45.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,S-sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.58,00:14:49.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What a cute room!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,00:14:53.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But it's not good for a witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.50,00:14:55.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,00:14:57.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,M-my room!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.95,00:14:59.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Gotta be black!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,00:15:00.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Even my bunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,00:15:02.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Witches' Sabbath.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,00:15:04.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We're gonna have a fun time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,00:15:07.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It flew!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.41,00:15:09.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Well, you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,00:15:12.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Marie, what are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.62,00:15:14.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I told you, I'm a witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.58,00:15:16.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm actually three hundred years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.41,00:15:17.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,00:15:18.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Witches live a really long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.25,00:15:22.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's amazing! I thought you were thirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,00:15:25.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't be rude. I still look like I'm eighteen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,00:15:27.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why'd you lie about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.33,00:15:30.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, how can I be a witch?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,00:15:36.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I fried up a mermaid and ate it to get my powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,00:15:37.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.29,00:15:42.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you're not going to eat it, then I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,00:15:45.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.12,00:15:47.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Marie liked playing tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.70,00:15:50.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She was crueler and a bigger liar than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.37,00:15:53.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do with those flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.41,00:15:55.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Boil them and make a tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.50,00:15:59.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Chamomile helps you fall asleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,00:16:01.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and marigold is good for your skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,00:16:06.45,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Even if you can't see it with your eyes, \Nthere are lots of things that have fantastic powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,00:16:08.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A witch draws out those powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.54,00:16:09.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.87,00:16:11.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I can do stuff like this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,00:16:17.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She was smart and playful,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,00:16:19.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and cute and fashionable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,00:16:23.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My young self was absolutely entranced by her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,00:16:26.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Marie is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,00:16:28.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She can use magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.66,00:16:30.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Marie is just good at stage tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.95,00:16:32.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I-it's real magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.83,00:16:34.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She's just playing with you, Koume.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.75,00:16:37.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Marie is a real witch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.79,00:16:39.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm getting really mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,00:16:42.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My mom and dad won't believe me at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.79,00:16:45.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's alright. It's just the way things are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.08,00:16:46.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.20,00:16:48.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've gotta focus on my studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.66,00:16:50.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,After all, I came to this country to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.08,00:16:53.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What are you studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.04,00:16:54.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Eastern magicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.08,00:16:59.37,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I'm traveling around the world on my broom \Nto learn about magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,00:17:01.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,so I can be the most powerful witch in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,00:17:04.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,00:17:07.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The most powerful witch in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.45,00:17:09.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But it's a secret, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.12,00:17:12.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Witches can't be cool unless they're mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.20,00:17:16.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's a lip-zipping spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,00:17:25.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If I show them your magic, they'll believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,00:17:27.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They'll believe you're a real witch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.12,00:17:33.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If I have Marie's broom, I should be able to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,00:17:39.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's for Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,00:17:42.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It'll definitely fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,00:17:47.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Save me, Marie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.70,00:17:51.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.70,00:17:53.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're braver than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.79,00:17:56.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But I think that's a bit too much mischief, Pu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,00:17:58.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Marie...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,00:18:05.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wow, it really does fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.25,00:18:07.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Of course it does. I'm a witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.41,00:18:13.04,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,But you can't show magic to anyone \Nthat doesn't believe in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.37,00:18:15.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's why you have to keep it a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.08,00:18:16.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you don't, there'll be a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.12,00:18:20.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why? It's so cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,00:18:25.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This is why you're still my petit Prune.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,00:18:27.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm not petit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,00:18:33.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,For a while, I didn't understand what she meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.58,00:18:37.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A mysterious disease is spreading through the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,00:18:41.08,Caption,,0,0,0,,EPIDEMIC
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,00:18:41.08,Caption2,,0,0,0,,Disease Rapidly Spreading
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.41,00:18:41.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, and the doctors are giving up on treating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.66,00:18:43.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's hold back from leaving the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,00:18:45.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Madam,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,00:18:47.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but there's a rumor going around town,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.08,00:18:52.62,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,that the witch staying with the Yukimi family \Nis what has brought this sickness upon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.91,00:18:54.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What? That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.62,00:18:57.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, but it's led to distrust in the Yukimi name...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.12,00:19:01.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It may end up affecting young Koume as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.08,00:19:06.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We do not doubt you in the slightest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,00:19:10.04,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,But for your sake, as well as ours, \Nit would be unwise for you to stay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,00:19:12.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, I understand, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.62,00:19:15.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll go back to France, for Prune's sake as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.16,00:19:16.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,00:19:18.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't look so blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.79,00:19:21.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm used to being treated as a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.91,00:19:24.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.12,00:19:28.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why?! You didn't do anything wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,00:19:31.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you're going to France, then I wanna go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.41,00:19:33.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll be your apprentice and learn how to be a witch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.45,00:19:37.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Please, take me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,00:19:41.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You know, becoming a witch isn't easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,00:19:45.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A crybaby like you could never be my apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,00:19:46.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I could!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,00:19:50.58,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I'd become a witch, and then \NI'd curse everyone who's mean to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,00:19:54.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's a pretty good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.16,00:19:55.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Maybe you've got what it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,00:19:57.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,00:19:59.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.54,00:20:06.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,...become the most powerful witch in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.41,00:20:09.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you do, I'll let you be my apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,00:20:13.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This is a cursed kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.75,00:20:17.25,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,A curse to give this little witch \Nlots of training and difficulties.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.29,00:20:21.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Take care, Mademoiselle Prune.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,00:20:23.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Marie...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,00:20:28.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And the witch went back to France.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.66,00:20:31.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I understand it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,00:20:35.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Marie wanted to tell me not to become a witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,00:20:39.54,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,That's why she gave me the impossible task \Nof becoming the most powerful witch in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.75,00:20:44.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But I won't do what she wants me to do. I won't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.29,00:20:46.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's why I came to Meirocho.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.16,00:20:49.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The most powerful witch in Meirocho...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.83,00:20:51.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,...a Rank 1 Urara?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,00:20:54.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, you want to be a Rank 1 Urara too, Koume?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.79,00:20:57.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I was trying to keep it a secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.87,00:20:59.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why are you even keeping that a secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.79,00:21:01.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then it wouldn't be cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.75,00:21:04.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Koume-chan, everyone, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.00,00:21:08.37,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Though they go by different names, \NUrara and witches are one and the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.50,00:21:11.62,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,They possess fantastic powers, \Nbut they have their downsides as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,00:21:16.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Outside of Meirocho, Urara are viewed much differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,00:21:20.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sometimes they're feared or ostracized.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.04,00:21:24.16,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Knowing all that, are you prepared \Nto continue your studies?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.62,00:21:26.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.00,00:21:31.37,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the most powerful Urara \Nin Meirocho- no, the whole country.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.58,00:21:36.87,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I'll help everyone and explain to them \Nthat witches aren't evil at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.29,00:21:39.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then I'll go to Marie with pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.04,00:21:42.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's my dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.70,00:21:44.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Koume, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.08,00:21:47.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I-it's not gonna work, I know it won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.00,00:21:51.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I... I trust Koume-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.54,00:21:52.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I feel like I can do it today!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.41,00:21:53.50,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I feel like I can do it today! \NGo! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,00:21:55.62,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I think we're definitely over the weight limit! \NGo! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.87,00:21:58.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here we go! Ready, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,00:22:01.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I realized something here in Meirocho.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.54,00:22:05.87,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,If there's something you can't get, \Nyou just have to reach out further...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.16,00:22:08.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then, you might be able to reach it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.37,00:22:13.08,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,It's okay to chase a dream \Nfrom which there's no turning back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.70,00:22:16.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So you better be ready for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.50,00:22:20.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My strong, kind, beloved witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.62,00:22:25.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.58,00:22:28.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I told you it wasn't going to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.62,00:22:29.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,One more try!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.54,00:22:50.41,Song,,0,0,0,,If I turn the corner, I wonder if I'll reach my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.95,00:22:55.12,Song,,0,0,0,,Getting lost and wandering in circles
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.12,00:22:58.95,Song,,0,0,0,,It'd be great if I could just run into you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.95,00:23:03.66,Song,,0,0,0,,There are some days when I don't have it altogether 1 to 10
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.91,00:23:06.95,Song,,0,0,0,,Which way should I go to get a happy ending?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.33,00:23:12.12,Song,,0,0,0,,From right to left, from like to love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.12,00:23:14.83,Song,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh, I'm in love with love! I'm in such a hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.83,00:23:18.87,Song,,0,0,0,,I want it badly, I can't get out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,00:23:23.20,Song,,0,0,0,,I'm looking
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.20,00:23:25.33,Song,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.33,00:23:27.79,Song,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen what you look like, but my heart's beating fast
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.79,00:23:29.70,Song,,0,0,0,,Kiss me in my imagination!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.70,00:23:31.83,Song,,0,0,0,,The moment we meet is a crash
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.83,00:23:33.95,Song,,0,0,0,,It gets a little complicated, that's fate
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.95,00:23:38.08,Song,,0,0,0,,Maybe, maybe you're lost too?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.20,00:23:40.83,Song,,0,0,0,,We can't see the end
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.83,00:23:45.83,Song,,0,0,0,,The maze that starts with romance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.12,00:23:51.00,Song,,0,0,0,,Will you find me in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.62,00:24:08.16,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Next time on Urara Meirocho, \N"Forbidden Things are Sometimes Totally Naked"!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.33,00:24:11.20,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,We can't tell fortunes, \Nbut there's something we have to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.20,00:24:12.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Captain Saku is so brave!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.75,00:24:16.08,Caption,,0,0,0,,"Forbidden Things are Sometimes Totally Naked"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.75,00:24:14.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Captain Saku is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.91,00:24:16.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That is all!
